{"tid":201852,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[羽毛球] 想搵班學有冇介紹","createTime":"2017-04-15T05:41:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-15T13:45:43.000Z","uid":87670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bc400fb63ae8a312021a0a02dd0941edf4d27aef","tid":201852,"uid":87670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T05:41:26.000Z","msg":"成年人想學羽毛球有冇介紹?<br />\n<br />\n上網搵過飛翔好似幾structural 好定唔好? 見佢有成人班一對二<br />\n價錢上好似比較OK 800~950/4堂<br />\n有D一個鐘600蚊好貴<br />\n<br />\n有冇人有介紹? 想上堂地方係九龍東最好"},{"pid":"5059d0d144440d5329b6561257378946d74f8fdc","tid":201852,"uid":87670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T05:48:32.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"0f2ca1c0780b319154358099c2484249591173ce","tid":201852,"uid":87670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T07:46:21.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"28c086a616a53358c6123e626d75ff868e35e0fa","tid":201852,"uid":18187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T07:49:06.000Z","msg":"自己搵個fd學吶，咁鬼貴"},{"pid":"4a439b8fbb1e3ed0d471c911e31c6f3d6300ab8f","tid":201852,"uid":74145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T07:56:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自己搵個fd學吶，咁鬼貴</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />想進步一定要學 <br />\n我諗你話揾個fd學應該係揾個fd練波"},{"pid":"dd5f50edd1cb3056196d03f1ef67abe5f109021a","tid":201852,"uid":87670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T09:07:00.000Z","msg":"200零蚊一個鐘, 一對二我覺得都ok<br />\n但上網搵唔到d人既comment 想睇下有冇人試過"},{"pid":"a3ffcdd1013d38b747e13bf76b31fe17e858c29f","tid":201852,"uid":22653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T09:10:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>200零蚊一個鐘, 一對二我覺得都ok<br />\n但上網搵唔到d人既comment 想睇下有冇人試過</blockquote><br />\n每人200 就得 <br />\n200 一個鐘應該揾唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n出面有名氣既都起碼收緊500一個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13d0f5b88b0e7cc0904ee64055cfca247c8dbe35","tid":201852,"uid":22653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T09:17:01.000Z","msg":"樓主你新手定有一定基礎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n新手既話你不如揾球會搞既訓練班打好過<br />\n如果唔識打你揾教練私人教好哂錢 比幾舊水人教揮拍同步法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你有咁上下水平先值得揾教練學技術"},{"pid":"5e4799e94d53e8adfc61c70bf016c94f6137331c","tid":201852,"uid":87670,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T10:44:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主你新手定有一定基礎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n新手既話你不如揾球會搞既訓練班打好過<br />\n如果唔識打你揾教練私人教好哂錢 比幾舊水人教揮拍同步法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你有咁上下水平先值得揾教練學技術</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n細個有學過 個陣嘗試考銅章失敗<br />\n<br />\n有咩訓練班推薦? 我以前都有參加過D訓練班, 但十幾廿人, 成堂先打得1-2條波...點練...所以我都係諗住小班D 起碼練波既時間都多D啦"},{"pid":"84ebedccb6c575975c48b287712a2366a3a3aa2d","tid":201852,"uid":22653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T12:48:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>樓主你新手定有一定基礎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n新手既話你不如揾球會搞既訓練班打好過<br />\n如果唔識打你揾教練私人教好哂錢 比幾舊水人教揮拍同步法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你有咁上下水平先值得揾教練學技術</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n細個有學過 個陣嘗試考銅章失敗<br />\n<br />\n有咩訓練班推薦? 我以前都有參加過D訓練班, 但十幾廿人, 成堂先打得1-2條波...點練...所以我都係諗住小班D 起碼練波既時間都多D啦</blockquote><br />\n你揾下近自己區有乜球會啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔係打多球就會進步的<br />\n初級訓練班教下揮拍步法岩你啦 <br />\n除非你要求係打到波就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  多球就幫到你"},{"pid":"40149abe95985167330f62e57ba1837e22907006","tid":201852,"uid":54617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T12:59:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>200零蚊一個鐘, 一對二我覺得都ok<br />\n但上網搵唔到d人既comment 想睇下有冇人試過</blockquote><br />\n每人200 就得 <br />\n200 一個鐘應該揾唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n出面有名氣既都起碼收緊500一個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n$500你講緊連埋場錢呀? 而家搵人book場要$100個場<br />\n利申教左幾年波<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df7fd7abff8a40d8ccf3988a7e94705727a44bd0","tid":201852,"uid":22653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T13:45:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>200零蚊一個鐘, 一對二我覺得都ok<br />\n但上網搵唔到d人既comment 想睇下有冇人試過</blockquote><br />\n每人200 就得 <br />\n200 一個鐘應該揾唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n出面有名氣既都起碼收緊500一個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n$500你講緊連埋場錢呀? 而家搵人book場要$100個場<br />\n利申教左幾年波<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n不嬲都唔包場錢<br />\n所以有錢仔先玩得起私鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}